 the OFS and the Secular Franciscan Vocation</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/what-is-formation_henri_ethier.pdf\">What is Formation?</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Workshop-Mary-Inspiration-for-Our-Life.pdf\">Workshop: Mary, Inspiration For Our Life</p></a>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Workshop-To-Live-a-Faithful-Life.pdf\">Workshop: To Live a Faithful Life</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Workshop-A-Pure-Heart.pdf\">Workshop: A Pure Heart</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Workshop-A-life-of-poverty-and-humility-and-a-pure-heart.pdf\">Workshop: A Life of Poverty and Humility and a Pure Heart</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Workshop-Invitation-to-life-in-a-fraternity.pdf\">Workshop: Invitation to Life in a Fraternity</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Workshop-A-life-of-responsibility-for-a-more-fraternal-world.pdf\">Workshop: A Life of Responsibility for a More Fraternal World</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Workshop-A-Life-pledged-towards-Justice-Carried-out-by-our-Work.pdf\">Workshop: A Life pledged towards Justice, Carried out by our Work</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Workshop-Commitment-to-the-OFS.pdf\">Workshop: Commitment to the OFS</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/References_material_from_approved_sources.pdf\">References: Material from Approved Sources</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Resources-of-Franciscan-Readings-for-Formation.pdf\">Resources of Franciscan Readings for Formation</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Notes-to-the-Formation-Director.pdf\">Notes to the Formation Director</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Introduction_to_excerpts.pdf\">Introduction to excerpts</a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','[NFEN] National Formation Objectives','','inherit',